{"tid":2252553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"越權做外交違基本法？張建宗與李家超晤德國駐港總領事，表達政府立場","createTime":"2020-10-21T14:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T14:25:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57c3968bd9c44a0d018b45fbc663ed87930732cf","tid":2252553,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555993-20201021.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555993-20201021.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=ec5cfed0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555993-20201021.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2bdc89a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555993-20201021.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n協助港人到外地尋求庇護的組織「避風驛」早前表示，一名在本港涉嫌暴動罪被捕的中文大學女學生，獲德國批出政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，如果報道屬實，特區政府表示強烈反對，要求外國政府，停止干預屬中華人民共和國內政的香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，德國駐港總領事下午應邀到政府總部，與政務司司長張建宗及保安局局長李家超會面。張建宗在會面時，已表達特區政府的立場，認為任何司法管轄區假借不同名義收留罪犯，是發出極度錯誤訊息，令人以為罪犯毋須負上刑責。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗重申，任何被控觸犯法例的人士，在香港都會獲公開及公平的審訊，香港法院亦會以獨立、公平和公正的態度，處理所有案件。"},{"pid":"44475d91f69e254a73370d804dfcc7d0c1a619ef","tid":2252553,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:05:12.000Z","msg":"特區政府帶頭搞港獨"},{"pid":"5400b4f7eafb1ecd2f46ed8f7e898b3aa8b44b3c","tid":2252553,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:05:28.000Z","msg":"外交事務關特區政府乜事？"},{"pid":"6e5b9d9923c5035f132f1918e657e0e736d2fe4b","tid":2252553,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:15:50.000Z","msg":"人地司法區關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637a1695ccb06a310e0cf55090289f20f451df03","tid":2252553,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:17:10.000Z","msg":"德國: 請勿干預我國內政"},{"pid":"978132eaf3277ca503bbc63e1336d8c4bfd4fe06","tid":2252553,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:25:29.000Z","msg":"well noted<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}